 PROJECT: Global Retail Sales & Profit Analysis Dashboard
Project Background

You are working as a Business Data Analyst for a global retail chain operating across regions, states, and product categories. The company wants a complete Excel-based analytics solution to understand sales performance, profitability, customer behavior, and discount impact.
Your job is to clean, transform, analyze, and visualize the dataset, then build a powerful dashboard for management.

DATASET
Columns Included:
Order ID
Order Date
Customer Name
Customer Type (New / Returning / VIP)
Segment (Consumer / Corporate / Home Office)
Region
Country
State
City
Category
Sub-Category
Product Name
Quantity
Unit Price
Discount
Shipping Cost
Sales
Profit
Order Priority
Payment Mode




PROBLEM STATEMENT
Design an Excel analytics system using the given dataset to answer the following:

Create Dashboards
Build a full Excel dashboard with slicers & interactive elements.
Dashboard 1 — Sales Performance
Include:
Total Sales (KPI card)
Total Profit (KPI card)
Profit Margin %
Sales by Region (Map chart or bar)
Sales Trend by Month (Line chart)
Category-wise Sales & Profit (Combo chart)
Top 10 Products (Bar chart)
Slicers:
Year
Category
Region
Customer Segment


Dashboard 2 — Customer Insights
Include:
New vs Returning customer ratio
Customer segment revenue share (Pie)
Top 10 customers by revenue
Average order value by segment
Discount impact (Scatter plot)
Slicers:
Year
State


Dashboard 3 — Product Profitability
Include:
Profitability heatmap by Category & Sub-Category
Discount vs Profit Margin scatter
High-loss product list (conditional formatting)
Category-wise YoY profit growth chart

